iiFoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDiiFoh.jpg&h=63fd3c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻雀雖小, 五臟俱全 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. reactor room 右邊中間空中有個 water detector 自動 會trigger 關reactor, 防止爆炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 有3個後備電池供電俾 reactor room water pump &amp; oxygen generator<br />\n3. 好多房都放左一件 潛水衣, 防止大入水時啲人會好快死. (不過暫時都係要人手控好架sub, 唔可以撞爆shell)<br />\n4. 4門coil gun 安排啲assistant 長期 開炮<br />\n<br />\n問題:<br />\n1. 啲電腦成日唔關門, 會令到樓下 ballast 右邊既 crafting room 入水<br />\n(我試過整計時自動關門既門, 但測試發現唔岩 multiplayer mode用, 狂按會出bug)<br />\n2. 架sub太細, 無安排位置放 loots <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到一地係 tool box, 同 outpost偷返來啲 鐵盒 lol"},{"pid":"e14b78bcf5e6d54f9962e680cbcbd047b7407ce8","tid":2099722,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:13:04.000Z","msg":"我睇既 DIY 潛水艇製作教學：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FnsRkbem5XI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFnsRkbem5XI&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=950e1352\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FnsRkbem5XI</a><br />\n<br />\n我架sub 入面既 自動關reactor 係自己研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 整好架sub之後，聽住background music慢慢將啲亂電線拉返直，好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159b0b83324f03d010a7baefac46a5217cf85bb6","tid":2099722,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9621fa89e1b6981145d3f03f078306d79430a611","tid":2099722,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af6822fb055b2e9c31f59d83f95a2ea69a50ad20","tid":2099722,"uid":168327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dee7a2ebde28cd01a3b13b41f5c1d413812c96a0","tid":2099722,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"一開始我見到都以為係, 簡體字呀嘛<br />\n但樓上話係芬蘭出<br />\n咁姐係啲fan made 在地化 o